WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.930
Leading geographically dispersed teams introduces friction known as social distance.

00:00:03.930 --> 00:00:07.860
The SPLIT framework serves as a diagnostic tool for identifying

00:00:07.860 --> 00:00:11.790
the root causes of this friction. You must analyze Structure,

00:00:11.790 --> 00:00:15.720
Process, Language, Identity, and Technology to pinpoint exactly where the

00:00:15.720 --> 00:00:19.650
systemic breakdown is occurring.
